      "0": "Also klnown as \"Elves' Bane\", this item was once ownded by an infamous highwayman.\n\nIn his day, Pandar of Scardale made quite a name for himself vexing the elves of Cormanthor forest.  To their annoyance he continually used the wood to escape the law; and with the aid of this girdle, the elves' arrows as well.  \n\nUnfortunately for Pandar, pit-traps \nand starvation proved a slower, but effective, substitution."
